name: Warring Shamans of Sunset
description: Hailing from the the regions surrounding Kharth’s Daggers, the Warring Shamans of Sunset might have… killed their former house leader? And that worries some people? Maybe? Yikes. Stay away from these guys. Now the defacto kings of the nearby woodlands, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
